🔵 Pattern 2: Modulo indexing
❓ “Am I just traversing cyclically?”
Use when:

* traversal continues cyclically

arr[i % n]

✔️ Used in:

* next greater element
* circular loops

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
🟡 Pattern 3: Break into cases
❓ “Is wrap vs non-wrap a decision?”
Use when:

* answer may wrap or not wrap
max circular subarray =
